    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that basically looks and smells brand new? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014it\u2019s in stunning, flawless shape. Seriously, it\u2019s been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and barely has a speck on it. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh-off-the-lot magic. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019m happy to chat!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance is complete: rod bearings have been replaced with WPC-treated shells, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with Turner plates to prevent floor failure. The suspension geometry is maintained via Bilstein PSS10 coilovers, providing exceptional damping control without compromising the chassis's inherent balance. Finished in Carbon Black over a pristine Nappa leather interior, this vehicle exhibits zero oil consumption and a perfectly linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. A truly turnkey specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Zero mechanical issues. Clean title.",
      "price": 44500.0,
