    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero chips, scratches, or swirl marks, while the factory-original wheels remain untouched. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, the controls feel crisp, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been meticulously garage-kept and serviced exclusively at the dealership with a full maintenance history available. Every electronic feature functions perfectly, and the engine bay is pristine. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that drives as perfectly as it looks.",
      "price": 46500.0,
